,{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"For example, you would confirm a SetupIntent when a customer hits the “Save” button on a payment method management view in your app.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"If the selected payment method does not require any additional steps from the customer, the SetupIntent’s status will transition to ","type":"text"},{"code":"STPSetupIntentStatusSucceeded","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":".  Otherwise, it will transition to ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"STPSetupIntentStatusRequiresAction"},{"type":"text","text":", and suggest additional actions via "},{"code":"nextAction","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":".","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Instead of passing this to "},{"code":"STPAPIClient.confirmSetupIntent(...)","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" directly, we recommend using "},{"code":"STPPaymentHandler","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" to handle any additional steps for you.","type":"text"}],"kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.stripe.stripe-payments-ui\/documentation\/StripePaymentsUI\/STPSetupIntentConfirmParams"}}}